metadata.name: Road to Geilen
metadata.description:
We all want utopia, no one is working for it, once there is an oath between us to create a better world and if there was consequences for breaking the oath, that time we might taste a little bit of utopia but there will be only few to taste the pleasure of Geilen, those are the ones who truly believe in the oath...

but what's Geilen ?  what's the oath?  what's the true utopia?

the past has told us, if not the future will tell us.
we just don't want to hear it or see it...

Bavugar
Thursday, 14th of April, 2022
